{"tid":1356711,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"727主題一定係反黑，反暴力，唔係要報復","createTime":"2019-07-23T14:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T04:32:34.000Z","uid":240372,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"25d63a2c3d143c27c39595d7f4b50bde097298f8","tid":1356711,"uid":240372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:32:28.000Z","msg":"大家千奇唔好用一個報復攬炒心態去，只會令自己做錯事，而家應該食住個勢上，把握對家失誤，令自己得分，<br />\n721元朗黑夜之後，公務員已經認唔住出聲，出黎支持示威者，雖然離成功仲好遠，但係只要我地727，唔好用暴力，等對家保衛家園呢個旗號打唔響，咁先係大把大把車落佢地塊面到。<br />\n至於好多人話要斷水斷電，我想講，咁會牽連好多平民百姓，作出呢d無差別攻擊只會令我地自降身份，水平同施襲者一樣。<br />\n我相信何君堯仲打完人咁招搖絕對就係一個撩交打策略，大家千奇唔好中計，727繼續和理非！"},{"pid":"a1acd910e777d5e87fd43f2baffc14ea840b390b","tid":1356711,"uid":240372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:33:39.000Z","msg":"朱凱廸：何君堯不是一個人，他是一種現象 挖墳拆祠堂=幫何君堯上彈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356075\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356075</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n詳情請睇呢到，唔好俾子彈人地，我地冇本錢行差踏錯"},{"pid":"19ff06b1a5cb9eb07522cc531028410f14aaae22","tid":1356711,"uid":165246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:34:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">１。全面撤回送中<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗暴動</span></span>"},{"pid":"a939abbdbcedd83421b9524b2be2929335700980","tid":1356711,"uid":20431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:35:18.000Z","msg":"宜家王法不行，日夜都好，黑警黑社會隨時可以打人，你行街發夢都隨時有危險<br />\n所以大家有必要學一啲基本parkour技巧！<br />\n大家可以入谷睇睇，會有教練義教parkour<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NQFyaRTdRi-hGADpSmHfLw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNQFyaRTdRi-hGADpSmHfLw&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4ZMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=0a1a93a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NQFyaRTdRi-hGADpSmHfLw</a>"},{"pid":"3115f5536aaa7544b756dce248f6cdf330f5a72e","tid":1356711,"uid":233520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:36:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">727 強烈建議由「元朗站」行到「大興站」散，千萬不要變成「民眾鬥民眾」，這是共產黨最喜愛的，如果雙方有傷亡，到時候是非曲直有理說不清，明益警察及政府可以借此收拾殘局！<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不要失焦，不要失焦，不要因小失大，報仇誤事，先搞掂狗及王志民<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n班鄉黑本來是收錢打人，現在玩大了，全部要交人及著草，冇事唔敢再打人，亦冇人再比錢佢地打人！"},{"pid":"10fad04367f7694b1e54aa2fe0af6c0de388594b","tid":1356711,"uid":192789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"19ff06b1a5cb9eb07522cc531028410f14aaae22","tid":1356711,"uid":165246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:34:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">１。全面撤回送中<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗暴動</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:37:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反對共產黨用黑社會制造白色恐怖</span>"},{"pid":"3e948e8f38e10963b4b7f04a22ae2aba0d7a3060","tid":1356711,"uid":8600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:41:26.000Z","msg":"認同真係唔好以報復心態去做,好易走火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69583c0f85bd6d5d2160fac63f72eb39311ce0d1","tid":1356711,"uid":240372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e948e8f38e10963b4b7f04a22ae2aba0d7a3060","tid":1356711,"uid":8600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:41:26.000Z","msg":"認同真係唔好以報復心態去做,好易走火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfaaa2743168422c48597b8b671861a724104863","tid":1356711,"uid":8600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:51:50.0